<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_surfaceSymmetry>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_surfaceSymmetry" ;
  rdfs:comment "Axiomatic derivation of the Surface Symmetry Theorem. Holds at all quantum levels: the composite P∘Π∘G is a well-typed morphism whenever G and P share the same state:Frame. Follows from the definition of the shared-frame condition and the type-equivalence algebra." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/surfaceSymmetry> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_CC_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_CC_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that a CompleteType T satisfies: resolution(x, T) terminates in O(1) for all x ∈ R_n. Follows from IT_7d: when χ(N(C)) = n and all β_k = 0, the resolver has no topological obstructions." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/CC_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_CC_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_CC_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that the ψ pipeline is monotone: each constraint application cannot increase the site deficit. Derived from the definition of the partition refinement order." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/CC_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_CC_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_CC_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that a CompletenessCertificate implies CompleteType: the certificate attestation is only issued when IT_7d holds, by construction of the CompletenessResolver." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/CC_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_CC_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_CC_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that the CompletenessAuditTrail witnessCount equals the number of CompletenessWitness records in the trail. Structural invariant of the audit accumulation protocol." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/CC_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_CC_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_CC_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that the CechNerve nerve computation is deterministic: the same constraint set always produces the same nerve topology. Follows from the nerve functor being a functor (functoriality)." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/CC_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof that neg(bnot(x)) = succ(x) in Z/(2^n)Z for all n ≥ 1. Derived symbolically from ring axioms: bnot is bitwise complement, neg is two's complement negation, succ is modular increment. The critical identity in universal form." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof that the ring carrier set size is exactly 2^n for all n ≥ 1. Follows from the definition of Z/(2^n)Z." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof that Landauer erasure cost scales as n × k_B T ln 2 at quantum level n. Follows from the thermodynamic interpretation: each bit erased from an n-bit ring costs k_B T ln 2." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof that the dihedral group D_{2^n} action on Z/(2^n)Z is faithful for all n ≥ 1. The stabilizer of any element is trivial under the full dihedral action." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof that canonical form rewriting terminates at all quantum levels. The rewriting system is terminating by lexicographic descent on the term complexity measure." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_6>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_6" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof that the completeness criterion χ(N(C)) = n generalizes to all quantum levels. Derived from the definition of the nerve construction and the Euler characteristic formula for simplicial complexes." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_QL_7>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_QL_7" ;
  rdfs:comment "Universal proof of the ring topology Euler characteristic identity: χ = 1 − n at quantum level n. Derived from the CW decomposition of the n-dimensional torus formed by the ring's cyclic group action." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/QL_7> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GR_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GR_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of binding monotonicity: freeRank(B_{i+1}) ≤ freeRank(B_i) for all i in a Session. Follows from the definition of the BindingAccumulator: each appended binding either pins sites or is a no-op; it never frees them." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GR_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GR_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GR_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that the empty session is the identity element of the session algebra: freeRank(B_0) = total site space. The empty accumulator has no pinned sites by definition." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GR_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GR_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GR_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of session convergence: a session terminates iff freeRank reaches its minimum (the maximum pinned by the given constraint set). Follows from the compactness of the site space and monotonicity." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GR_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GR_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GR_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof that disjoint bindings compose without site conflict: if two bindings address disjoint site sets, their composition is well-defined and their union is also a valid binding." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GR_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GR_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GR_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of contradiction detection correctness: ContradictionBoundary fires iff there exist bindings b, b' in the same Context with the same address, different datum, and same constraint. This is the minimal condition for type contradiction." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GR_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of nerve realisability: for any target profile with χ* ≤ n and β₀* = 1, there exists a ConstrainedType whose constraint nerve realises the target. Follows from the constructive synthesis algorithm." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of minimal basis bound: the MinimalConstraintBasis for the IT_7d target has size exactly n. Follows from the site-by-site construction and the minimality criterion." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of synthesis monotonicity: adding a constraint never decreases the Euler characteristic of the constraint nerve. Follows from the nerve inclusion principle." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of synthesis convergence: the TypeSynthesisResolver terminates in at most n steps. Follows from monotonicity (TS_3) and the finite site budget bound." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of synthesis-certification duality: a SynthesizedType achieves IT_7d iff the CompletenessResolver certifies it as CompleteType. The duality follows from the shared topological criterion." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_6>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_6" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of Jacobian-guided synthesis efficiency: the Jacobian oracle reduces expected steps from O(n²) to O(n log n). Follows from the information content of the Jacobian at each synthesis step." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_TS_7>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_TS_7" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of unreachable signatures: β₀ = 0 is unreachable by any non-empty ConstrainedType. Follows from the nerve connectedness of non-empty constraint sets." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/TS_7> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/InductiveProof> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of lift unobstructedness criterion: WittLift T' is CompleteType iff the spectral sequence collapses at E_2. Follows from the Leray spectral sequence of the quantum level extension." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/baseCase> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_1_base> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/inductiveStep> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/validForKAtLeast> "0"^^xsd:integer ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/BitwiseInduction> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/InductiveProof> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of obstruction localisation: a non-trivial LiftObstruction is localised to a specific site at bit position n+1. Follows from the local-to-global structure of the constraint nerve." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/baseCase> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_2_base> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/inductiveStep> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_2_step> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/validForKAtLeast> "0"^^xsd:integer ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/BitwiseInduction> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/InductiveProof> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of monotone lifting: basisSize(T') = basisSize(T) + 1 for trivially obstructed lifts. Follows from the minimal basis construction at Q_{n+1}." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/baseCase> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_3_base> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/inductiveStep> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_3_step> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/validForKAtLeast> "0"^^xsd:integer ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/BitwiseInduction> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/InductiveProof> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of spectral sequence convergence bound: the spectral sequence converges by page E_{d+2} for depth-d configurations. Follows from the filtration length of the constraint nerve chain complex." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/baseCase> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_4_base> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/inductiveStep> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_4_step> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/validForKAtLeast> "0"^^xsd:integer ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/BitwiseInduction> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/InductiveProof> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of universal identity preservation under quantum lifts: every universallyValid identity holds in the lifted ring. Follows from the universal validity definition and ring extension properties." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/baseCase> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_5_base> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/inductiveStep> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/validForKAtLeast> "0"^^xsd:integer ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/BitwiseInduction> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_6>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/InductiveProof> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_6" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of ψ-pipeline universality for quantum lifts: the ψ-pipeline produces a valid ChainComplex for any WittLift. Follows from the functorial construction of the chain complex." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/baseCase> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_6_base> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/inductiveStep> <https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_6_step> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/validForKAtLeast> "0"^^xsd:integer ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/BitwiseInduction> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_1_base>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_1_base" ;
  rdfs:comment "Base case for QLS_1 at Q0: lift unobstructedness holds trivially for 8-bit rings where the constraint nerve is contractible." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "false"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Composition> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_2_base>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_2_base" ;
  rdfs:comment "Base case for QLS_2 at Q0: obstruction localisation holds at the 8-bit level where sites are directly inspectable." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "false"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Composition> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_2_step>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_2_step" ;
  rdfs:comment "Inductive step for QLS_2: if obstruction is localised at Q_k, the local-to-global structure of the constraint nerve preserves localisation at Q_{k+1}." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Composition> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_WLS_3_base>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_WLS_3_base" ;
  rdfs:comment "Base case for QLS_3 at Q0: monotone lifting basis size increment holds trivially for 8-bit to 16-bit extension." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/WLS_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "false"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
