<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of holonomy group containment: HolonomyGroup(T) ≤ D_{2^n}. Follows from the fact that all constraint applications are dihedral group elements." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of additive flatness: additive constraints (ResidueConstraint, DepthConstraint) generate only the identity in D_{2^n}. Follows from the additive structure of the dihedral action." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of dihedral generation: neg and bnot together generate D_{2^n}. Follows from the standard presentation of the dihedral group by involutions." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of holonomy-Betti implication: non-trivial holonomy implies β₁ ≥ 1. Follows from the fact that a non-trivial monodromy requires a topological loop in the constraint nerve." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of CompleteType holonomy: IT_7d (β₁ = 0) implies trivial holonomy (FlatType). Follows from MN_4 contrapositive: trivial holonomy ← β₁ = 0." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_6>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_6" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of monodromy composition: the monodromy map is a group homomorphism from the loop space to D_{2^n}. Follows from the composition of dihedral group elements." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MN_7>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MN_7" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of TwistedType obstruction class: a TwistedType always contributes a non-zero class to H²(N(C(T')); ℤ/2ℤ) for any WittLift T'. Follows from MN_4 and the obstruction theory of dihedral torsors." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MN_7> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_PT_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_PT_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of PT_1: product type site additivity. siteBudget(A × B) = siteBudget(A) + siteBudget(B). Follows from the definition of ProductType as an independent concatenation of site spaces." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/PT_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_PT_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_PT_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of PT_2: product type partition factorisation. partition(A × B) = partition(A) ⊗ partition(B). Follows from the tensor product structure of constraint nerves over independent site spaces." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/PT_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/EulerPoincare> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_PT_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_PT_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of PT_3: product type Euler characteristic additivity. χ(N(C(A × B))) = χ(N(C(A))) + χ(N(C(B))). Follows from the Künneth formula applied to the join of constraint nerves." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/PT_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Composition> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_PT_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_PT_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of PT_4: product type entropy additivity. S(A × B) = S(A) + S(B). Follows from PT_1 (site additivity) and TH_1 (S = freeRank × ln 2)." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/PT_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_ST_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_ST_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of ST_1: sum type site budget maximum. siteBudget(A + B) = max(siteBudget(A), siteBudget(B)). Follows from SumType requiring capacity for the larger variant." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/ST_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_ST_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_ST_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of ST_2: sum type entropy. S(A + B) = ln 2 + max(S(A), S(B)). The ln 2 term accounts for the variant discriminant bit; the max reflects that only one variant is active at a time." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/ST_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_1: context temperature. T_ctx(C) = freeRank(C) × ln 2 / n. Derived from TH_1 normalized per site." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_2>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_2" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_2: saturation degree. σ(C) = (n − freeRank(C)) / n. Definitional identity." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_2> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_3>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_3" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_3: saturation monotonicity. Corollary of SR_1 through order-reversing SC_2." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_3> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_4>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_4" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_4: ground state equivalence. Four equivalent conditions for full saturation derived from SC_2, TH_1, SC_1." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_4> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_5>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_5" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_5: O(1) resolution guarantee at saturation. Derived from SR_2 and FreeRank.isClosed at freeRank = 0." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_5> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_6>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_6" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_6: pre-reduction of effective budget. Derived from session-scoped site reduction at partial saturation." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_6> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/RingAxiom> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_GS_7>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_GS_7" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of SC_7: thermodynamic cooling cost. n site-closures at Landauer cost each via SR_1 + TH_4." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/GS_7> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/verified> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/strategy> <https://uor.foundation/proof/Simplification> .

<https://uor.foundation/proof/prf_MS_1>
  a owl:NamedIndividual , <https://uor.foundation/proof/AxiomaticDerivation> ;
  rdfs:label "prf_MS_1" ;
  rdfs:comment "Proof of MS_1: connectivity lower bound β₀ ≥ 1. Formalisation of TS_7." ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/provesIdentity> <https://uor.foundation/op/MS_1> ;
  <https://uor.foundation/proof/universalScope> "true"^^xsd:boolean ;
